skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Get travel inspiration via your flash briefing - helping you decide where to go on your next travel adventure. We share a new destination daily with tips and recommendations on what to do there.

Where will you go next?

Brought to you by Inspire Flyer - inspireflyer.com 
Flight search and travel features to inspire you for the next adventure.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
